Subject: Blocking Writer's Block
Description: The dreaded writer's block. What is it, and how do you get rid of it? Our panelists will ponder this pernicious plague upon creativity, and how to root it out of your writing practice. Writer's block can be beaten. We've done it.  Speakers include:Fred Paffhausen, Michael W. Lucas, Colleen Nye, Vik Walker - Track: Lit  - Duration: 1 hour
